{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a new Shopify Featured Collection section inspired by premium fashion brands like COS, ARKET, Fear of God, Zara Studio, Massimo Dutti, and Apple.
    
    Do NOT use the default Dawn Featured Collection layout.
    
    Design a completely custom section with a clean editorial luxury aesthetic while keeping full Shopify functionality.
    
    Objective
    
    Build a premium Featured Collection section that feels modern, minimal, luxurious, and fashion-focused.
    
    The design should emphasize:
    
    Editorial typography
    Large whitespace
    Premium image presentation
    Smooth interactions
    Mobile-first responsiveness
    Fast loading
    Fully customizable in Shopify Theme Editor
    
    Use:
    
    Liquid
    CSS
    Vanilla JavaScript only
    
    No external libraries.
    
    Section Header
    
    Layout:
    
    Left Side
    
    Small Eyebrow Label
    
    THE EDIT
    
    Style
    
    Uppercase
    11px
    Letter spacing: 0.25em
    Font weight: 600
    Color: #C23A45
    
    Main Heading
    
    Featured Selection
    
    Style
    
    Elegant editorial serif font (use theme serif font if available)
    Similar to Canela / PP Editorial New / Cormorant Garamond
    Desktop: 46px
    Mobile: 34px
    Weight: 400
    Color: #111111
    
    Subheading
    
    Handpicked pieces from our latest drop.
    
    Style
    
    Theme body font (Inter if available)
    16px
    Color #666
    
    Right Side
    
    Button
    
    SHOP ALL
    
    Style
    
    Uppercase
    Letter spacing: .35em
    Thin underline
    Underline expands smoothly on hover
    Layout
    
    Maximum Width
    
    1400px
    
    Products
    
    Desktop
    
    4 columns
    
    Tablet
    
    3 columns
    
    Mobile
    
    2 columns
    
    Spacing
    
    Desktop
    
    100px top
    80px bottom
    
    Mobile
    
    48px
    
    Large editorial whitespace throughout.
    
    Product Card
    
    Design an elegant premium product card.
    
    Requirements
    
    White background
    No visible borders
    Rounded image container (18px)
    Image background #F6F6F6
    Overflow hidden
    
    Hover Animation
    
    Card
    
